Update Cargo.lock

This updates the Cargo.lock file for Clippy:

- parking_lot 0.11.2 -> 0.12 (now 2 versions in parking lot)
- rustfix 0.6.0 -> 0.6.1 (now only one version left)
- compiletest_rs 0.7.1 -> 0.8
- clap 2.34.0 -> 3.1.1
